@Sjors [wrote](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/29775#issuecomment-2056345622):
> If anyone wants to deploy a faucet, let me know and I'll send some coins... unless someone reorgs me.

Yes, I'd be happy to set up a Testnet4 faucet similar to [Alt Signet Faucet](https://alt.signetfaucet.com/). Please send me some testnet coins to `tb1p4tp4l6glyr2gs94neqcpr5gha7344nfyznfkc8szkreflscsdkgqsdent4` on [Testnet4](https://mempool.space/testnet4/address/tb1p4tp4l6glyr2gs94neqcpr5gha7344nfyznfkc8szkreflscsdkgqsdent4).

